Condor::

As soon as Skullgrin left the cells' area Condor woke up, he looked 
around, he felt better enough better to attempt to escape. Condor 
stood up and walked towards the bars. To leave this place, he had to  
destroy the energy bars and avoid several dangers...

But how could he destroy the bars?
